<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ferretería Online</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        footer h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #e67e22;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.2px;
        }
        footer p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            color: #ccc;
        }
        footer p a {
            color: #e67e22;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        footer p a:hover {
            color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <footer>
        <h1>Neque porro quisquam est qui dolorem ipsum quia dolor sit amet, consectetur, adipisci velit</h1>
        <p>Neque porro quisquam est qui dolorem ipsum quia dolor sit amet, consectetur, adipisci velit. <a href="#">Más información</a></p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
